msgid "Backend Developer specializing in Python Django, with strong experience in building scalable web applications and automation tools. Skilled in Django Rest Framework, FastAPI, Docker, WebSocket, PostgreSQL, and Telegram Bot development."
msgstr "Backend-разработчик, специализирующийся на Python Django, с большим опытом создания масштабируемых веб-приложений и инструментов автоматизации. Навыки: DRF, FastAPI, Docker, WebSocket, PostgreSQL и разработка Telegram-ботов."

msgid "I love solving complex problems, writing clean code, and building products that make a real difference. I'm also passionate about teaching and sharing knowledge."
